{"tid":975012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋不在席未能處理檢討單程證動議　主席宣布休會","createTime":"2019-01-09T10:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T10:18:32.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53bf701f3f66b5bc6baa8ba760966ec78343a1db","tid":975012,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"立法會休會。休會前未有處理公民黨議員楊岳橋提出「檢討單程證政策」的議員議案。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥表示，由於楊岳橋當時不在席，所以不會處理。楊岳橋在梁君彥宣布休會後到會議廳外，隨即到會議廳內了解情況。<br />\n本周立法會會議的議程已完結，明日立法會會舉行行政長官答問會。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋事後就事件鞠躬道歉. 他解釋當時在辦公室, 因專注收看政制及內地事務局局長聶德權, 介紹國歌法的記者會, 因而疏忽沒及時返回會議室提出動議.<br />\n他說, 會繼續關注有關單程證的問題, 亦會在今年內以《私人條例草案》形式跟進.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190109/photo/bkn-20190109164338449-0109_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190109172654\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190109164338449-0109_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190109172654&h=34b9807e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a83871732eb2d84032cad469aeb1586264ceef39","tid":975012,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190109/59123565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190109%2F59123565&d=GVks3%2F%2FXRBcl6rEY6c16IPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=eb8379a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190109%2F59123565&h=09c9e684\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190109/59123565</a>"},{"pid":"d12a0fe78e1267345d3150c742d6600c558e167e","tid":975012,"uid":9681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"屌大陸奸細"},{"pid":"d464c5f78af8eb6ba40a818d8307a611f7e9bc6a","tid":975012,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"休會唔好咩？"},{"pid":"b5b41ea54110acecdc3b6b0d06bdb58fb45131f2","tid":975012,"uid":80103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"關鍵缺席喎又"}]}